fr.sorbonne_u.components.helpers

Interface CVMDebugModesI

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CVMDebugModes

    public interface CVMDebugModesI
    The interface CVMDebugModesI marks values of debug modes to ease their extension by end users.

    Description

    This interface is implemented by the enumeration CVMDebugModes as well as the type of the values of the set in the variable AbstractCVM.DEBUG_MODES. Hence, this setting allows programmers to extend it with their own debugging modes.

    Invariant

     invariant              true

    Created on : 2018-08-28

    Author:
    Jacques Malenfant
